<li id="cite_note-175"><b><a href="#cite_ref-175" title="">^</a></b> <a href="/wiki/Freeman_Dyson" title="Freeman Dyson">Freeman Dyson</a>, <i>The Sun, The Genome, and The Internet</i> (1999) Oxford University Press. <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0195139224" class="internal">ISBN 0-19-513922-4</a></li>
<li id="cite_note-176"><b><a href="#cite_ref-176" title="">^</a></b> <i>Greetings, Carbon-Based Bipeds!</i> (1999) <a href="/wiki/Arthur_C._Clarke" title="Arthur C. Clarke">Arthur C. Clarke</a>, Voyager <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0002246988" class="internal">ISBN 0-00-224698-8</a></li>
